headline.print_headline: Russia Voices Concern Over 'Militaristic Statements' From Kiev
headline.main: Russia Voices Concern Over 'Militaristic Statements' From Kiev

lead_paragraph: The Russian Foreign Ministry expressed concern on Wednesday about "militaristic statements" from Kiev after acting President Oleksander Turchinov said Ukraine's armed forces were on full military alert in case of a Russian invasion.
